{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Datebase/mariaDB","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"acdc398f-dd7d-5521-8ead-e3e1f0da386d","html":"<p>mysql 삭제하기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo rm <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>rf <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>usr<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>local<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>var<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>mysql\nsudo rm <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>rf <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>usr<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>local<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token builtin\">bin</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>mysql<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\nsudo rm <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>rf <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>usr<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>local<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Cellar<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>mysql</code></pre></div>\n<p>mariaDB 설치하기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">brew install mariadb</code></pre></div>\n<p>mariaDB 서버 키기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">mysql<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>server start</code></pre></div>\n<p>mariaDB에 접속하기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">mysql <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">u</span> root</code></pre></div>\n<p>만약 Access denied 에러가 발생한다면</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">ERROR <span class=\"token number\">1698</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">28000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Access denied <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> user ‘root’@‘localhost’</code></pre></div>\n<p>아래 방법대로 하기!!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo mysql <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">u</span> root <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>컴퓨터 비밀번호 입력해서 접속한 다음\nuse mysql<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nselect <span class=\"token function\">password</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>‘설정할 비밀번호‘<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nalter user’root’@‘localhost’ identified by ‘비밀번호’<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"django-에서-runserver시-did-you-install-mysqlclient-라고-나올-때\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#django-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-runserver%EC%8B%9C-did-you-install-mysqlclient-%EB%9D%BC%EA%B3%A0-%EB%82%98%EC%98%AC-%EB%95%8C\" aria-label=\"django 에서 runserver시 did you install mysqlclient 라고 나올 때 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>django 에서 runserver시 “Did you install mysqlclient?” 라고 나올 때</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>settings.py 에 아래 내용 추가</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> pymysql\npymysql<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>version_info <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">13</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"final\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\npymysql<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>install_as_MySQLdb<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>pip install pymysql 설치</li>\n<li>mariaDB 접속해서 database 생성\ncreate database insa character set utf8mb4 collate utf8mb4<em>general</em>ci;</li>\n<li>python manage.py migrate</li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Datebase/mariaDB","tagSlugs":["/tag/maria-db/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-05-25","description":"mac에서 mysql 삭제 후 mariaDB 설치하기","tags":["mariaDB"],"title":"mysql 삭제 후 mariaDB 설치하기","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Datebase/mariaDB"}}}